<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="10" type="way of life">
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Way of life.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Size range - 3.5 mm to 6.0 mm; adults of this genus are found singly at night on wet leaf litter at the margins of swamps and medium-sized rivers, and on dry trails in primary rainforest.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
